    LVWIT 4inch LED Recessed Light with E26 Conversion Kit, 5CCT

    Higher adaptability Color Selectable, ONE kit for all the room in your house.
    Dimmable The lightness could be adjusted from 5% to 100%.
    Energy Efficient 7watt light serves as 85watt incandescent lamp.
    Easy Installation with E26 Conversion Kit, the Recessed Light could be installed like bulbs(T24 Connector still available).
    Light Color 2700/3000/4000/5000/6000K (from warm to cool)
    Brightness 700lumen @3000k &100%
    Wattage 7watt (85watt equivalent)
    Voltage 120v
    Hz 60Hz
    CRI 80
    Illumination Angle 100
    Usage Temperature -15C~40C&10%-85%
    lifespanh 20000

      Theses are really cool and make changing out Style of lighting so easy! I used these in my house to replace regular bulbs which are directly above my kitchen cabinets and they fit perfectly! I am still surprised how easy it was to change the look of your decor with something like these lights! All you do is connect the wire from the light to the wire that has the E26 attachment, then screw them into place. Pending of course the type of space you have to click these into place they should work no problem! I will provide some pics or a video to show how i replaced some inverted bulbs with these and also right next to that space i have some Track Lighting and i used these lights in the exact same way! So cool and so easy! Once the lights are installed, if you wanted to change your mind about the mood of lighting all you need to do is pop the lights back out and toggle between the color temperatures till you find one that suits your mood, then just pop them back in place. SO EASY!, I love that. All you really need to pay attention to is the Size of the hole of the space which you intend to replace the bulbs with these. The sides of these lights have little CLIPS which are meant to clip into drywall and hold them up but as you can see from my photos you can use these in a variety of other ways as well. Very easy five stars from me and i really do recommend these as they are super user friendly!
